  <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About Us</h1>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <p class="lead text-muted">
        Welcome to <strong class="brand-name">Skill Swap</strong>! We are
        dedicated to creating a vibrant community where individuals can share
        their skills and knowledge while learning from each other. Our platform
        serves as a bridge, connecting people who are eager to teach and those
        who are ready to learn, fostering a culture of collaboration and
        continuous growth.
      </p>
      <p>
        At <strong class="brand-name">Skill Swap</strong>, users can explore a
        variety of skills ranging from coding and photography to cooking and
        gardening. Our user-friendly interface makes it easy for anyone to find
