    <p class="lead">
      At <strong class="brand-name">Skill Swap</strong>, our mission is to
      empower individuals through skill-sharing and collaboration. We strive to
      create an inclusive environment where learners and mentors can connect,
      fostering a sense of belonging and shared purpose. We believe that skill
      exchange is not just about teaching and learning; it's about building
      relationships and creating a supportive community that thrives on the
      diverse talents of its members.
    </p>
    <p>
      We are committed to making personal development accessible and enjoyable
      for everyone. Our vision is to inspire individuals to unlock their
      potential, embrace new challenges, and cultivate a lifelong love for
      learning. Together, we can transform the way we share knowledge and grow,
      one skill at a time!
    </p>
  </div>
